Interface ParseHandler

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    CodeHandler, JavaCodeHandler, JavadocHandler
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JavaCodeHandlerDebugImpl, JavaCodeHandlerImpl, JStatistics.StatisticsJavaCodeHandler

    public interface ParseHandler
    Defines the interface exposed by a Parse Handler, that is the handler receiving messages from a CodeParser.
